replies.body:
Hey,
Not going to lie if you want to climb the best way is to just keep on playing and learning from each game. Grind until you get where you want, there is no easy way imo. Just don't flame and try your best to be supportive to your team regardless if they are nice or not, oh and if someone is aggravating you just mute them and unmute later in the game just incase they say something important relating to the game. Oh and if you haven't already try to practice more champs and get used to all the roles so regardless of what one you end up getting you can play it well.
Good luck man!{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
